Package javadoc

Class Employee

java.lang.Object
javadoc.Employee
All Implemented Interfaces:
EmployeeSalary
Direct Known Subclasses:
Janitor, Teacher
public abstract class Employee extends Object implements EmployeeSalary
*Short description of the class This tag can only be utilized in the class header

This is an abstract class that models Employees. It is intended to define the hierachy base of our model Teacher and Janitor would extend it It forces subclasses to implement the employeeFunction method: employeeFunction()

For some algorithms the String API is needed API String Subclasses Extending this class are:
  • Teacher
  • Janitor
Since:
1.0
Version:
1.2
Author:
Carlos Cano, Serena Lopez
